# Scraper & Metrics Layer Rules

## Absolute Prohibition

**Zero imports from `openai` or `src/lib/ai` anywhere in this layer.**

These directories must remain AI-free so metrics stay deterministic and testable independently.

## Pure Functions

All metric extractors follow the same signature:

```ts
// Input: Cheerio root ($) + page URL
// Output: a single typed value — no side effects
export function extractWordCount($: CheerioAPI): number { ... }
export function extractHeadings($: CheerioAPI): HeadingCounts { ... }
```

## Fetch Requirements

In `src/lib/scraper/fetch-page.ts`:
- Timeout: 10 seconds (use `AbortController`)
- User-Agent: `'Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; WebAuditBot/1.0)'`
- Max redirects: follow up to 5 (default fetch behavior)
- Throw typed `FetchError` on network failure or non-2xx status

