```ts
// CTA detection heuristic — inherently approximate.
// Counts: <button>, [role=button], <a> with class containing btn/cta/button/action,
// <a> with text matching known CTA phrases.
// Limitation: misses JS-rendered buttons and CSS-only styled CTAs.
```

## Alt Text Calculation

```ts
// altTextPercent: % of images WITH a non-empty alt attribute
// Returns 0 when imageCount === 0 (avoids division-by-zero)
const altTextPercent = imageCount === 0
  ? 0
  : Math.round((imagesWithAlt / imageCount) * 100);
```
